OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNo fuel shortage, says     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftransport secretary        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%title3
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, There is "no shortage of fuel" and     
OL,6, people should be "sensible" and only   
OL,7, fill up when they need to, Transport   
OL,8, Secretary Grant Shapps has said.       
OL,10,FIt comes as long queues and closed     
OL,11,Fpumps continue at some filling         
OL,12,Fstations.                              
OL,14,FMr Shapps said he was introducing a    
OL,15,F"big package" of measures, including   
OL,16,Ftemporary visas for HGV drivers, to    
OL,17,Fhelp the situation.                    
OL,19,FHe blamed leaks by hauliers for        
OL,20,Ftriggering a "rush on petrol stations".
